text: Tserendorjiin Dagvadorj (born 25 October 1940) is a Mongolian archer. Dagvadorj competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics and the 1980 Summer Olympics.Tserendorjiin Dagvadorj == References == Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Mongolian archers Category:Olympians for Mongolia
title: Tserendorjiin Dagvadorj
